did.abstract: The University of Kentucky Libraries. Special Collections Research Center. University Archives collection on University of Kentucky Athletics Broadsides (dated 1967-2015, undated; .61 cubic feet; 1 flat box and 2 oversized folders) comprise posters and flyers collected by university archivists and university records managers documenting University of Kentucky men's and women's athletic teams, coaches, players, games, and seasons.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Collection is open to researchers by appointment

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Collection is arranged by sport, then chronologically within decade subseries.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: 2023ua042: [identification of item], University of Kentucky Athletics Broadsides, 1967-2015, University of Kentucky Libraries Special Collections Research Center.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The University of Kentucky Libraries. Special Collections Research Center. University Archives collection on University of Kentucky Athletics Broadsides (dated 1967-2015, undated; .61 cubic feet; 1 flat box and 2 oversized folders) comprise posters and flyers collected by university archivists and university records managers documenting University of Kentucky men's and women's athletic teams, coaches, players, games, and seasons. Some of the broadsides advertise companies or products. Basketball, football, baseball, gymnastics, soccor, and rifle posters, among others, are inlcuded.

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: Property rights reside with the University of Kentucky. The University of Kentucky holds the copyright for materials created in the course of business by University of Kentucky employees. Copyright for all other materials has not been assigned to the University of Kentucky. For information about permission to reproduce or publish, please contact the Special Collections Research Center.
